org.apache.poi.xssf.usermodel

Class XSSFShapeGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.xssf.usermodel.XSSFShape
      • org.apache.poi.xssf.usermodel.XSSFShapeGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<XSSFShape>, Shape, ShapeContainer<XSSFShape> 

    public final class XSSFShapeGroup
extends XSSFShape
implements ShapeContainer<XSSFShape>
    This object specifies a group shape that represents many shapes grouped together. This shape is to be treated just as if it were a regular shape but instead of being described by a single geometry it is made up of all the shape geometries encompassed within it. Within a group shape each of the shapes that make up the group are specified just as they normally would.(${t_1158b57928c94f0091571c7586cbcc01})
